::DeathScythe/Ramulus::

DeathScythe yells, shots peircing his hide, fur, and scales. The shot from 
SnowCat hits his upper neck, his body going limp and jets going out. 
DeathScythe smashes into the ground, laying still where he fell.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus puts away his gun, walking into the clearing. He looks at SnowCat. 
"Are you allright?"
